commands.name: block
commands.description: Blocks a level ID | Usage: "%pblock <Level ID>" to block a specific ID

commands.name: blockuser
commands.description: Blocks a user | Usage: "%pblockuser <Username>" to block a specific user

commands.name: gdping
commands.description: Pings the Geometry Dash servers | Usage: "%pgdping"

commands.name: info
commands.description: Gets the specified level's information, default is current selected level | Usage: "%pinfo" | "%pinfo <Position>"

commands.name: move
commands.description: Moves the specified level from one position to another | Usage: "%pmove <Level ID> <Position>"

commands.name: next
commands.description: Gets basic information about the next level in the queue | Usage: "%pnext"

commands.name: position
commands.description: Finds your position in the queue | Usage: "%pposition" | "%pposition <Number of Requested Level>"

commands.name: queue
commands.description: Gets the current level request queue | Usage: "%pqueue" | "%pqueue <Page>"

commands.name: remove
commands.description: Removes a level from the queue (only works on your own levels, unless mod) | Usage: "%premove <Position>"

commands.name: request
commands.description: Sends requests | Usage: "%prequest <Level ID>" | "%prequest <Level Name> by <User>" (Use quotation marks to search by exact name) | "%prequest <Level Name>"

commands.name: song
commands.description: Finds the current level's song information | Usage: "%psong" | "%psong <Position>"

commands.name: top
commands.description: Moves a specified level to the top of the queue | Usage: "%ptop <Level ID>"

commands.name: unblock
commands.description: Unblocks a level ID | Usage: "%punblock <Level ID>" to unblock a specific ID

commands.name: unblockuser
commands.description: Unblocks a user | Usage: "%punblockuser <Username>" to unblock a specific user

commands.name: wronglevel
commands.description: Removes the latest sent level by you | Usage: "%pwronglevel"
